<HEADLINE> UK Unemployment Hits Record Low </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LONDON, August 16 (Xinhua) -- Unemployment in Britain fell to a
record low while average earnings continued to fall, official
figures released Wednesday showed.
</P>
<P>
Data from the Office for National Statistics saw that the
number of people unemployed and claiming benefit was down last
month by 22,700 to 1,069,800.
</P>
<P>
