<TEXT>
<P>
CHENGDU, August 16 (Xinhua) -- China is taking on the ambitious
task of becoming a major producer and consumer in the world floral
market, said a top official from the Chinese Florists Association
(CFA) here today.
</P>
<P>
Jiang Zehui, chairwoman of the CFA and president of the Chinese
Research Institute of Forestry, made the remark at the opening
ceremony of a high-level meeting of the association.
</P>
