SPH led decliners of the day shedding 50 cents to close at 28.4
Singapore dollars. SPH 100 retreated 20 cents to close at 28.5
dollars. F &AMP; N slid 15 cents to end at 6.7 Singapore dollars.
</P>
<P>
Dealers noted that property stocks were broadly higher ahead of
earnings reports. 
