<HEADLINE> Chinese Treasuries Quiet on Wednesday </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 16 (Xinhua) -- China's treasury bond market
stayed narrow today as domestic A-share market rallied further,
consolidating investor's confidence in stocks.
</P>
<P>
The combine transaction value totaled 903 million yuan, 60
percent less than the figure of yesterday.
</P>
<P>
