</P>
<P>
-- Sudan's Foreign Minister Moustafa Ismail, in a telephone
interview with the Cairo-based Sout al-Arab radio service Tuesday,
praised the efforts exerted by Egypt and Libya to achieve national
reconciliation in Sudan. 
