the U.S., so dialog and relations with the country would solve no
problem, the leader said Tuesday in a meeting with Foreign
Ministry officials, including Iranian ambassadors stationed abroad.
The main objective of Washington in proposing dialog is to prepare
the ground for imposing its stances and materialize its wishes,
Khamenei pointed out. (US-Iran-Relations)
</P>
