with the sub in the night operation and had to be brought to
surface to restore its life-support system. The multipurpose "
Kursk" went down to the bottom of the Barents Sea on Sunday while
attending a routing exercise of the Russian Northern Fleet. It is
not clear whether there are any casualties among the servicemen
