<HEADLINE> GM Revs Up for Shares in China </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, August 16 (Xinhua) -- The first vehicle of the Jinbei-
GM Automobile Co., Ltd. will roll off the assembly line on
December 15, China Daily reported.
</P>
