flagship" development in the city's automobile sector and the
municipal government of the northeast China city will give the
company better services to ensure its success.
</P>
<P>
Jinbei-GM intends to make more vehicles for the Chinese market.
</P>
<P>
The venture will initially put out 30,000 vehicles per year and
then expand to 50,000 a year. 
