fair from October 24 to 28.
</P>
<P>
The Second Shanghai International Industry Fair will let
visitors see the city's latest high-tech achievements, including
those in biomedicine, environmental protection, information and
new materials. It also lets participants make business deals,
according to today's "China Daily".
</P>
