<HEADLINE> Argentine Stocks Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BUENOS AIRES, August 16 (Xinhua) -- The leading Merval index on
the Buenos Aires Exchange Wednesday closed down 1.17 percent at
473.31 points compared with Tuesday's 478.94 points.
</P>
<P>
